-- Auchan, Renault-Nissan to Form Banks in Russia, Kommersant Says
-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 2012-05-21T05:55:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-21/auchan-renault-nissan-to-form-banks-in-russia-kommersant-says.html
Groupe Auchan SA and the Renault-
Nissan alliance plan to launch bank projects in cooperation with
their financial partners in  Russia  that include Credit Europe
Group and Unicredit Group,  Kommersant  reported, citing several
people familiar with the plans.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow at 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
